    {
      "id": "c7d9264c-08ed-4c0d-af46-bd00eeaad038",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$(\\cos (\\pi/7) + i \\sin (\\pi/7))(\\frac{1-i\\sqrt{3}}{2})(1+i) = \\sqrt{2}(\\cos(5\\pi/84)+i\\sin(5\\pi/84)),$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\((\\cos (\\pi/7) + i \\sin (\\pi/7))(\\frac{1-i\\sqrt{3}}{2})(1+i) = \\sqrt{2}(\\cos(5\\pi/84)+i\\sin(5\\pi/84)),\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "9e828915-dd7d-4890-8a2f-a03b771733d2",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$(1-i)(\\cos (\\pi/5) + i \\sin (\\pi/5))(\\sqrt{3}-i) = 2\\sqrt{2}(\\cos(13\\pi/60)-i\\sin(13\\pi/60)),$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\((1-i)(\\cos (\\pi/5) + i \\sin (\\pi/5))(\\sqrt{3}-i) = 2\\sqrt{2}(\\cos(13\\pi/60)-i\\sin(13\\pi/60)),\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7b565862-3199-4b81-8019-aed2002e89ea",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\frac {\\sqrt{2}(\\cos (\\pi/12) + i \\sin (\\pi/12))}{1+i} = \\frac {\\sqrt{3}-i}{2}.$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac {\\sqrt{2}(\\cos (\\pi/12) + i \\sin (\\pi/12))}{1+i} = \\frac {\\sqrt{3}-i}{2}.\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "945e00ac-3e39-4bb1-ba6c-4aafcba5ad72",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Il s'agit juste d'appliquer la formule de Moivre :\n$$e^{i\\theta} = \\cos \\theta +i \\sin \\theta ;$$\nainsi que les formules sur les produits de puissances :\n$$e^{ia}e^{ib} = e^{i(a+b)}\\text{ et  } e^{ia} / e^{ib} = e^{i(a-b)}.$$",
        "html": "<p>Il s’agit juste d’appliquer la formule de Moivre : <span class=\"math display\">\\[e^{i\\theta} = \\cos \\theta +i \\sin \\theta ;\\]</span> ainsi que les formules sur les produits de puissances : <span class=\"math display\">\\[e^{ia}e^{ib} = e^{i(a+b)}\\text{ et  } e^{ia} / e^{ib} = e^{i(a-b)}.\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
